In this special Web Summit episode of the Horizons of Leadership podcast, we sit down with Brendan Smith, VP of Growth at GetFresh Ventures.

At GetFresh Ventures, Brendan has worked on more than 60 early-stage engagements across SaaS, marketplaces, and digital health, helping founders close $25M+ in funding and generate over $115M in revenue. His work blends strategy and execution, from ICP and GTM design to operational sprints and investor readiness.

